729807f-a.title: Richmond: Van Duzer Street - Smith Terrace
729807f-a.text:
Van Duzer Street, at the N.E. corner of Smith Terrace. The house was owned by K. Sessup in 1874; by L. D2 Jonge in 1898, and by Clara Poel in 1907. Dates refer to maps on which the owners' names appear.
February 25, 1931
P. L. Sperr
